"""""""""""
"  Basic  "
"""""""""""
" Splits
nnoremap <C-j> <C-W>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-W>k
nnoremap <C-h> <C-W>h
nnoremap <C-l> <C-W>l
nnoremap √ü <C-W>=

" Move by wrapped line
nnoremap <silent>j gj
nnoremap <silent>k gk
nnoremap <silent>gj j
nnoremap <silent>gk k
vnoremap <silent>j gj
vnoremap <silent>k gk
vnoremap <silent>gj j
vnoremap <silent>gk k
inoremap <silent><up> <C-o>gk
inoremap <silent><down> <C-o>gj

" Tab Movement
nnoremap <S-h> gT
nnoremap <S-l> gt
nnoremap <A-h> gT
nnoremap <A-l> gt
" In GVim
nnoremap <A-1> 1gt
nnoremap <A-2> 2gt
nnoremap <A-3> 3gt
nnoremap <A-4> 4gt
nnoremap <A-5> 5gt
nnoremap <A-6> 6gt
nnoremap <A-7> 7gt
nnoremap <A-8> 8gt
nnoremap <A-9> 9gt
" In urxvt
nnoremap <Esc>1 1gt
nnoremap <Esc>2 2gt
nnoremap <Esc>3 3gt
nnoremap <Esc>4 4gt
nnoremap <Esc>5 5gt
nnoremap <Esc>6 6gt
nnoremap <Esc>7 7gt
nnoremap <Esc>8 8gt
nnoremap <Esc>9 9gt

" Paste and Yank to System Register
nnoremap √º "+p
nnoremap √ú "+Y
vnoremap √º "+y
vnoremap √ú "+p
inoremap √º√º <C-r>+

" Macro execution
nnoremap Q @

